STATE
v.
VANCE 2018-1722 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 6, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appellant's amended motion for appointment of counsel, amended motion for preparation of statements, praecipe, and notice to the court reporter for a complete copy of the transcript of proceedings, and amended request for oral argument denied. Kennedy, J., would deny appellant's motions as moot.
